{"tid":725724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲記唔記得轉筆最流行嘅時候?","createTime":"2018-07-01T23:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T07:46:41.000Z","uid":163153,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9bcbd267a0170c7dbe05df75a70b5631ee1b1836","tid":725724,"uid":163153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T23:01:06.000Z","msg":"我記得嗰陣小學有一排興轉筆 班房個個都拎住支筆喺度轉 有啲仲話3蚊一支嘅大頭狗筆好轉啲<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/065621_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F065621_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0b6b21c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者最普通pilot嘅ball pen已經好好轉<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/065909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F065909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e417c9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰時好多筆都因為成日跌搞到冇墨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想pro啲嘅直接買專用筆<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/065956_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F065956_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=74d631d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想當年我都有一支 但我冇人地轉得咁勁 不過都拎黎寫字扮下野咁 <br />\n<br />\n唔知大家依家拎起支筆仲會唔會手痕轉多幾下咁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0d39ce7816877cd017c68e0c967ba94120ffa9","tid":725724,"uid":283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T23:02:00.000Z","msg":"好似有個網教轉筆<br />\n好多花式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68acd2bafdb580a8d3ec6711f6147f9c454e814","tid":725724,"uid":171509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T23:02:00.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"40391a41ce93d9e16888e53a972bec5a3aae2f1d","tid":725724,"uid":163153,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T23:04:51.000Z","msg":"嗰陣上堂成日都聽到啲筆跌落地 啪 一聲 次次都唔同位傳黎 老師就鬧 唔係唔比你地轉 但係你地轉就唔好跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  然後lunch time 佢改簿嗰陣見到佢拎住支紅筆轉 大家都<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  放咗學上youtube仲有好多教學片睇添"},{"pid":"3ca836d616d78ea5adf702898083d079df7f9980","tid":725724,"uid":163153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a0d39ce7816877cd017c68e0c967ba94120ffa9","tid":725724,"uid":283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T23:02:00.000Z","msg":"好似有個網教轉筆<br />\n好多花式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T23:06:10.000Z","msg":"細個多數都上youtube睇 但都係學唔到 睇到學校老師係支筆兜過隻拇指再返返轉頭 嗰陣已經覺得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1481ab41d6e94fa6cf59e4d7f85ac7dbb8bf5ff2","tid":725724,"uid":163153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b68acd2bafdb580a8d3ec6711f6147f9c454e814","tid":725724,"uid":171509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T23:02:00.000Z","msg":"唔會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T23:14:37.000Z","msg":"以前見啲人一拎起支筆隻手就不自覺轉筆 依家真係冇見到啦"},{"pid":"a32f30124f4bcf92dac1cab74d63d06aba63c27a","tid":725724,"uid":163153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T23:39:44.000Z","msg":"太早開post冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7dd503b324b9dfaeb7de1b2eb96fd973b486ec0","tid":725724,"uid":1403,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T23:41:56.000Z","msg":"成日上hkpsa睇人教砌mod<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nseven g7 mod<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal